imdb.plot outline: The story focuses on five women between 30 and 50 years old who, through bankruptcy, know each other and this will cause an emotional, economic and affective change in their lives. It will take a new and unexpected path in their lives so they can reflect in depth on their personal stories. Something like a second chance. The last to fall in love, perform, build a family, follow the vocation, heal wounds or simply overcome fears, those that paralyze and do not allow advance. After all, they are not perfect, they are braves.
imdb.title: Guapas
plot: The story focuses on five women between 30 and 50 years old who, through bankruptcy, know each other and this will cause an emotional, economic and affective change in their lives. It will take a new and unexpected path in their lives so they can reflect in depth on their personal stories. Something like a second chance. The last to fall in love, perform, build a family, follow the vocation, heal wounds or simply overcome fears, those that paralyze and do not allow advance. After all, they are not perfect, they are braves.
